َّذِي","tier":"q100","transliteration":"alladhīna"},{"id":"ac-1:7:3","surahNum":1,"ayahNum":7,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"أَنْعَمَ","targetTranslation":"you bestowed blessing (on عَلَيْهِمْ)","ayahArabic":"صِرٰطَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ غَيْرِ ٱلْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","ayahEnglish":"The path of those upon whom You have bestowed favor, not of those who have earned [Your] anger or of those who are astray.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["Grant grace","Show kindness","Give blessing"],"pos":"V","lemma":"أَنْعَمَ","tier":"q600","transliteration":"anʿamta"},{"id":"ac-1:7:5","surahNum":1,"ayahNum":7,"wordNum":5,"arabic":"غَيْر","targetTranslation":"other than (in genitive case)","ayahArabic":"صِرٰطَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَنْعَمْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ غَيْرِ ٱلْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","ayahEnglish":"The path of those upon whom You have bestowed favor, not of those who have earned [Your] anger or of those who are astray.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["upon","despite","through"],"pos":"N","lemma":"غَيْر","tier":"q100","transliteration":"ghayri"}]